description:
Branson is a big, hunky, 20-year-old straight guy who works as an Emergency Medical Technician.

So I, with my dirty mind, immediately conjured up images of him in a tight little uniform driving around rescuing cute girls.

When I shared my little fantasy with him, he laughed and said, "That happens once in a while, but more often it's little old ladies!"

Branson likes to play baseball, and he's done a few professional modeling stints.
title: Branson
